data.description: Welcome to 3305 Garden Point Dr. Pulling up you'll be greeted by the stamped walkway and an assortment of landscapes that include a healthy cherry blossom tree. Right as you step in you'll appreciate its inviting floor plan because of the open concept, crown molding, tall ceilings and the pleasant ambience. This eye-catching breakfast bar was made for enjoying a meal or cocktail while the matching fireplace makes the living room a cozy space to enjoy snuggles and coco. The kitchen gives so much to admire from mosaic trimmed backsplash, granite countertops, staggered cabinets, and a stylish wine rack. Outback is a stone paved covered patio and enough space to use your imagination without breaking the bank. Your primary bedroom is nestled on its own side of this home to give you a space for peaceful living. For your convenience Desert Garden Park is within walking distance while schools, shopping, eateries and countless other amenities are just a short drive away. Call to view this lovely home today.
